OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with a few breaks offering some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells to end the day.
OL,8,FOften cloudy overnight with some
OL,9,Fpatchy drizzle over the hills. Frost-
OL,10,Ffree.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FRather cloudy on Wednesday
OL,13,Fwith further outbreaks of mostly light
OL,14,Fdrizzle, and limited brighter breaks.
OL,15,FA more organised band of rain likely
OL,16,Fto arrive from the northwest towards
OL,17,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
