OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FPatchy frost initially on Thursday,
OL,7,Fbut then fine with some sunshine.
OL,8,FTurning unsettled over the Easter
OL,9,Fweekend with showers or longer spells
OL,10,Fof rain. Some strong and gusty winds
OL,11,Ftoo.
